            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/811/123.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 03:30:39 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 11 月 17 日消息，数魅无线领夹麦克风现已开售，该款无线麦克风配备 LED 液晶屏显、支持 50 米无线传输，<strong>售价 1198 元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="858" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/e4d073bd-f93b-4e2a-b347-0e83feb3ad53.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNS5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="745" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/I6kfSqT" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/101835/38/54050/49619/672dcb4bF057a316f/d300fa4377236c82.jpg" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">数魅无线领夹麦克风</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> LED 液晶屏显 | 50 米无线传输</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">首发 1198 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1309" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/3650791e-0766-4429-9c4c-2cc18e7eec7e.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNS5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="745" /></p><p>据介绍，数魅无线领夹麦克风内置<strong>智能主动降噪芯片</strong>，采用&nbsp;2.4G 传输协议，支持&nbsp;360° 全指向收音；其内置 <strong>3 重自适应降噪</strong>（升级低切 + ENC 环境降噪），宣称可对不同频率噪音作削减，保留人声。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="848" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/a44c7cd1-d4be-44b9-b4ba-ac4c12608a21.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNC5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="743" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="986" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/95dcb239-4627-4204-be0f-5fccda38be0d.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNC5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="741" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1244" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/171997b4-1195-4690-917c-03a60588e5a3.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNC5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="743" /></p><p>该款麦克风支持&nbsp;<strong>50m 距离</strong>不断频、声音不断连传输；其自带充电盒，官方<strong>宣称续航 8 小时</strong>；麦克风配备无线发射器（重约 16g），号称“支持兼容市面上 99% 的设备”，无需配对、即插即用。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1054" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/ebc23b6c-ce45-49b8-a6a5-1bb4b5bf9160.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNC5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="742" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1151" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/18f23a0f-6f3a-43e0-8eff-00162a4a1eb5.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNC5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_170,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="744" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">IT之家附数魅无线领夹麦克风产品参数如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1217" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/90f8a595-7b5c-4490-a76e-afaaefc930f0.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDExMy5wbmc=,t_100,g_6,y_0,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="数魅无线领夹麦克风开售：LED 液晶屏显、50 米无线传输，首发 1198 元" width="735" /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
